data.title: Lebanese don't look southern european at all [Archive]
data.meta_description:
I was curious about the Lebanese because a lot of threads are showing them similar to Southern Europeans. Well, that's not true. I've found pics of lebanese footballers from Beirut. They can't pass in Southern Europe as a whole. Some can do it individually, but they are a minority.
